      "name": "Latch On",
      "type": "ability",
      "system": {
        "description": "<p>&nbsp;The demon attempts to grab onto a target. Make an attack roll against the<br>target. On a success, instead of dealing damage, the demon gains a special condition, Latched.&nbsp;While Latched, the demon has access to the Seed special ability, but also has -2d to defense rolls.</p>",
