    {
      "name": "Seed",
      "type": "ability",
      "system": {
        "description": "<p>The demon attacks a target it is Latched onto, attempting to make the target a host&nbsp;for its young. If successful, the target takes the normal Wound and is injected with eggs. The eggs&nbsp;can be removed surgically or allowed to hatch. The surgery to remove them requires a TN 6 Medical&nbsp;check by someone with 1 rank in Medical. If the target is attempting to perform it on himself, he will&nbsp;have a -2d penalty. The eggs will hatch in 3 days and will inflict 1d 5/W5 Wounds on the host as the&nbsp;larva eat their way out. Anyone that witnesses this must make a Resolve save as if resisting Fear 6.</p>",
        "action": "full"
      },
